article.description: — Ant Nelson had 20 points as Manhattan narrowly defeated The Citadel 77-74 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Nelson scores 20 to carry Manhattan over The Citadel 77-74
article.linkText: Nelson scores 20 to carry Manhattan over The Citadel 77-74
article.story: CHARLESTON, S.C. -- — Ant Nelson had 20 points as Manhattan narrowly defeated The Citadel 77-74 on Tuesday night. Jose Perez had 18 points and six assists for Manhattan (8-3). Elijah Buchanan added 13 points. Samba Diallo had 10 points. Hayden Brown had 19 points for the Bulldogs (6-5). Jason Roche added 18 points. Brent Davis had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
